b'             Dear Students,    Tomsk Polytechnic University is a National Research university which places special emphasis on advanced engineering education, creation of resourceefficient technologies, internationalization and integration of research and academic activities.  TPU was founded in 1896 and it is the second in ranking of the Russian Ministry of Education and Science.TPU offers a number of degree programs mostly in Russian and partly in English language. You can find information about TPU at     The Contest "Your First Success" is aimed to provide 10 State academic Scholarships of Russia exclusively for education at TPU Master Degree Programs in English.  Tomsk Polytechnic University proposes 2 programs to IITM students:  1. "Biomedical Sciences and Engineering"; (the program is about all forms of Medical Tomography), developed in cooperation with Siberian State Medical University  2. "Nuclear Power Installation Operation&quo;t; (the program is about Nuclear Reactor Operation),developed in cooperation with Rosatom State Corporation    All tests will include 30 questions: 10 questions in Math, 10 questions in Physics, and 10 questions in specific field of particular program (Electronics for the first program and Nuclear Physics for the second program).   The maximum time for Contest is 50 min. (&#'

